Name: Car Crash Online
About the game: Try to imagine what it means to be crushed, flattened, smeared on the asphalt! Break up your cars and enemies cars. Crash, crumble and blow up all sorts of obstacles and barriers. Dead loops, trampolines and much more await you in the Car Crash Online! Take a break from the routine and immerse yourself with total peace of fun, destruction and utter mayhem. Features: -Excellent Graphics -Realistic Physics collisions and destruction -A Large variety of tricks from the simplest to the most complex -High Speed ​​and an unforgettable drive -Multiplayer -Up to 20 Bots!
